data.description: Experience luxury in this pristine 2013 Pulte-built "Cameron" home in Estero's esteemed Preserve at Corkscrew community. Originally owned & recently updated with fresh interior paint & new bedroom carpets, this residence boasts high-volume ceilings, an open great room, & numerous upgrades including a whole house generator with 500 gal in-ground propane tank, impact-resistant windows, elegant wood flooring, plantation shutters & custom closets. Comprising three bedrooms, three full baths, a versatile den, & a three-car garage, it offers ample living and storage space. The kitchen is a true chef's dream, featuring two spacious islands-perfect for culinary creations and entertaining guests, while the owner's bathroom boasts a frameless shower door, adding a touch of elegance to your daily routine. The property features an expansive screened-in lanai & a private backyard adjacent to a nature preserve, ideal for relaxation or entertainment. Located in a premier gated community with low HOA fees, this home enjoys access to resort-style amenities and is conveniently situated near beaches, shopping, & transportation, all while being outside the flood zone for added peace of mind.
